REMARK 300 REMARK: BIOLOGICAL_UNIT: MONOMERTHE GLYCINE CLEAVAGE                 
REMARK 300  SYSTEM IS COMPOSED OF FOUR PROTEINS:P, T, L,                        
REMARK 300  AND H. THE H CHAIN WAS STUDIED HERE. THIS                           
REMARK 300  COMPONENTSHUTTLES THE METHYLAMINE GROUP OF GLYCINE                  
REMARK 300  FROM THE P PROTEINTO THE T PROTEIN. THE H                           
REMARK 300  CHAIN CONTAINS A COVALENTLY-BOUNDLIPOYL COFACTOR.                   
